keyMappings:
map H previousTab
map L nextTab
map , goBack
map . goForward
unmap T
map t Vomnibar.activateTabSelection
map ' Marks.activateGotoMode
searchEngines:
gh: https://github.com/search?q=%s&type=repositories GitHub
awiki: https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php?search=%s ArchWiki
man: https://man.archlinux.org/search?q=%s&go=Go ArchManPages
goid: https://www.google.co.id/search?q=%s GoogleId
g: https://www.google.com/search?q=%s Google
br: https://search.brave.com/search?q=%s Brave
ddg: https://duckduckgo.com/?q=$s DuckDuckGo
rdt: https://www.reddit.com/search/?q=%s Reddit
aur: https://aur.archlinux.org/packages?O=0&K=%s AUR
pacman: https://archlinux.org/packages/?q=%s pacman
w: https://www.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Search&search=%s Wikipedia
